Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at them, so young and carefree.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.70,0:00:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't know how good they have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.94,0:00:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Youth is wasted on the young.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.86,0:00:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And wisdom is wasted on the old.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.45,0:00:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you suppose they're talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.34,0:00:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, if I were to guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.90,0:00:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey everyone! Look at me! I'm neglecting my studies!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.36,0:00:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I the team leader? I'm only twelve!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.83,0:00:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, all I do is mope.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.53,0:00:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm too young to know how tough life really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's my problem? Who knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.69,0:00:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Yang! Let's fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.87,0:00:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not that bad, Winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.72,0:00:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That is exactly how they sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.00,0:00:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Grown-ups have it so easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.70,0:00:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They can do anything they want and never get in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.91,0:00:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruby, I don't think that's how being a grown-up works.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.68,0:00:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ruin this for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.06,0:00:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, where was I? Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.80,0:01:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go eat heaps of dessert!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.85,0:01:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Agreed! And let's throw all the vegetables in the trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.28,0:01:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! And afterwards, let's stay up as late as we want!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.01,0:01:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Curfews are for chumps!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.00,0:01:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister would never use the word "chumps".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.77,0:01:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That is exactly how adults talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I give the tummy rubs! I'm a good girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I sneak the treats. I'm the best girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.22,0:01:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a chew toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.86,0:01:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the Yang! Let's fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.48,0:01:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Penny! I was watching my fourth favorite show!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.46,0:01:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to meet my new friends, Ruby!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.78,0:01:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ew, outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.08,0:01:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But all the cool kids are indoors watching TV and lying on a comfy sofa like a sog!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.34,0:01:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,ESCAPE!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:02:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I calculated a ninety-three percent probability you would try that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.72,0:02:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, fine, where are these mysterious friends of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.53,0:02:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They are all around us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.66,0:02:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
